<li sourcefile="client-side/using-gulp.md" sourcestartlinenumber="297" sourceendlinenumber="297"><p sourcefile="client-side/using-gulp.md" sourcestartlinenumber="297" sourceendlinenumber="297">In <strong>Task Runner Explorer</strong>, verify that the <strong>min</strong> task has been set to run <strong>Before Build</strong>.</p>
