</li>
<li sourcefile="client-side/using-gulp.md" sourcestartlinenumber="307" sourceendlinenumber="307"><p sourcefile="client-side/using-gulp.md" sourcestartlinenumber="307" sourceendlinenumber="307">Press <strong>F5</strong> to run the application in a browser.</p>
