<li sourcefile="client-side/using-gulp.md" sourcestartlinenumber="309" sourceendlinenumber="311"><p sourcefile="client-side/using-gulp.md" sourcestartlinenumber="309" sourceendlinenumber="309">In the browser window, right-click the page and select <strong>View Source</strong> to view the HTML for the page.</p>
<p sourcefile="client-side/using-gulp.md" sourcestartlinenumber="311" sourceendlinenumber="311">Notice that the stylesheet links point to the minified CSS files.</p>
